title: Yogalates Firm Fit and Flexible
description:
Firm fit and flexible focuses completely on strengthening and stretching increasing flexibility, enhancing that streamline shape to Sculpt and elongate your muscles with out building bulk, So as to release tension within the muscles which enhances nerve function enabling the body to function in a balanced way. With the instruction focusing on the breathing this will facilitate graceful controlled movements.

With its unique design includes everything necessary for optimizing flexibility/fitness and endurance of mind and body.

The yogalates method develops the body uniformly. Corrects bad posture, lengthens and stretches the musculature, restores and increases physical vitality, stimulates the mind and elevates the spirit.
